        <div class="msgSubject">Changes I'd like to see this update...</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-19 12:23:10   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-129019099073848271" id="quote-129019099073848271" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-129019099073848271" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=10&amp;mid=129019099073848271&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=129019099073848271&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_129019099073848271" onclick="followToggle('add','129019099073848271')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
